Step 1: Stop and disable all container services
bash
Copy
Edit
systemctl stop docker
systemctl disable docker
systemctl stop podman
systemctl disable podman
ðŸ”¹ Step 2: Remove all Docker and Podman packages
bash
Copy
Edit
sudo dnf remove -y docker* podman* containerd* runc
ðŸ”¹ Step 3: Clean up leftover files and links
bash
Copy
Edit
rm -f /usr/bin/docker
rm -rf /var/lib/docker
rm -rf /var/lib/containerd
rm -rf /etc/docker
Optional cleanup:

bash
Copy
Edit
rm -rf /run/docker
rm -rf /usr/libexec/docker
âœ… Now Install Docker 28.1.1
ðŸ”¹ Step 4: Create a working directory
bash
Copy
Edit
